224
00:12:13,670 --> 00:12:15,170
Tidak ada, jawab saja.

225
00:12:15,630 --> 00:12:17,940
Kalau begitu, merah.

226
00:12:18,200 --> 00:12:18,970
Merah?

227
00:12:19,210 --> 00:12:21,110
Begitukah? Sudah kuduga.

